name: First Words
description: Headphones on. Tap to play / pause. First Words is a generative audiovisual collage played in real-time on your browser's built-in speech and tone synthesizers. Best on desktop Chrome / Safari. Also supports Firefox / iOS. Limited support for Android [voice switching may fail]. "Voices" Track 2. Words from Owen R., age 14 months. Idlebit 2021.
